asket instead of measuring cup on mixing bowl lid and cook <b>15 min\/100°C\/\/speed 0.5<b>. Meanwhile, toast bread slices.  Serve Moroccan harira hot drizzled with olive oil and garnished with reserved chopped coriander and plain yoghurt, with toasted white bread."}],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","55m","4 portions"]}